==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Knights fee
<hw>Knight's fee</hw>. <fld>(Feudal Law)</fld> <def>The fee of a knight;
specif., the amount of land the holding of which imposed the obligation
of knight service, being sometimes a <er>hide{1}(b)</er> or less,
sometimes six or more hides.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knight Templar</ent>⟦br⟧
